Syntax: flurry <target>

Channels all remaining chi energy into a rapid sequence of strikes against
a single target. Each point of chi spent produces one additional attack,
making flurry highly damaging when your chi pool is full.

Effects:
  - Repeatedly executes one_hit() against the target, once per chi point.
  - Drains your entire chi pool in the process.
  - Activates a 30-round cooldown preventing reuse.

Because flurry consumes all your chi, activating it when your chi pool is
low produces few hits. Maximize effectiveness by building chi before use.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Must have at least 5 chi points available.
  - Must have the Flurry skill learned.

See also: shelp flurry chakra spinfist phantomfist
